{"tid":939680,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"7日7夜大阪遊 一齊入黎plan行程啦","createTime":"2018-12-13T10:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T14:05:05.000Z","uid":101732,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"828de6bed2ca9d4886928746a5dfd44fa6d299fe","tid":939680,"uid":101732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:11:01.000Z","msg":"我新年後會去一個星期大阪 第一次去<br />\n會盡量去埋京都 奈良 神戶<br />\n而家淨係諗到大綱 未知實際會點 大家比下意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n6點早機到關西機場<br />\n我見有得係機場坐船去神戶<br />\n打算會留一日 滑雪 浸溫泉 食野 行街<br />\n神戶有冇邊間溫泉酒店住得過？<br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n返大阪<br />\n都係不外乎係心齋橋附近行街 食野 買野<br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n環球影城<br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n搭車去京都 只係知道清水寺(我知裝修緊)同伏見稻荷神社<br />\n下午去奈良 除左影鹿仲有咩做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一日去哂兩個地方會唔會太趕<br />\n<br />\nDay 5 6 7<br />\n大阪？唔知有咩行程 求介紹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10e29b3dd0d22b95de22a39bdb275ad4a265c80","tid":939680,"uid":101732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa44f8ea7f180ace55e8697e8e8cf182664c263","tid":939680,"uid":35746,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"先京都 後大阪是常識吧"},{"pid":"8a8048544826eddc814a9dafb23d6c376fa365e3","tid":939680,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:26:34.000Z","msg":"同一日係冇可能京都+奈良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你睇下地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3781f3c1dae44227f51052b077cf2868c9d19729","tid":939680,"uid":9231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"你仔定女 幾多人去 同邊個去先<br />\n奈良就得鹿 其實就好快睇完 女就可能耐d"},{"pid":"5a966bc8a2bcaa49595ce58df63bd761448c1a2b","tid":939680,"uid":101732,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"3781f3c1dae44227f51052b077cf2868c9d19729","tid":939680,"uid":9231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"你仔定女 幾多人去 同邊個去先<br />\n奈良就得鹿 其實就好快睇完 女就可能耐d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:30:52.000Z","msg":"我同女朋友兩個<br />\n我都見奈良得鹿 所以迫埋京都一日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d503f2accfa4cfd3d97e9c4d91df4628e3079f","tid":939680,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:30:58.000Z","msg":"留名跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b189c216c7f24cd229ab4b08a526722c7303ed","tid":939680,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:31:01.000Z","msg":"Day 4趕到傻<br />\n加埋冬天好快天黑 （大約4:30） 你去到奈良可能鹿都未見到就黑<br />\n京都可以嘅話留一晚啦<br />\n嵐山， 哲學之道，二條城，平安神宮 好多野睇"},{"pid":"41e4742061488af94824de249ae591b150ea9e38","tid":939680,"uid":101732,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8a8048544826eddc814a9dafb23d6c376fa365e3","tid":939680,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:26:34.000Z","msg":"同一日係冇可能京都+奈良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你睇下地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"我見奈良冇乜野做 google map搭車一個鐘囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分開一日去奈良好似嘥左時間 搭多程車去"},{"pid":"bc83a412bd2abec4a220a9debd8a81fd6c6cc077","tid":939680,"uid":101732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9b189c216c7f24cd229ab4b08a526722c7303ed","tid":939680,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:31:01.000Z","msg":"Day 4趕到傻<br />\n加埋冬天好快天黑 （大約4:30） 你去到奈良可能鹿都未見到就黑<br />\n京都可以嘅話留一晚啦<br />\n嵐山， 哲學之道，二條城，平安神宮 好多野睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:35:15.000Z","msg":"咁我應該會聽大家意見 分兩日京奈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n奈良可以好快返大阪"},{"pid":"805bae502e6e29abbb69fa7027c1d287166e92ce","tid":939680,"uid":71303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:38:03.000Z","msg":"飛"},{"pid":"4defa00f1113a35f65d406d56d4d78467aefa292","tid":939680,"uid":122592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:43:07.000Z","msg":"day4太趕"},{"pid":"d73fd2f72d8092cb60a8a1fdb030e86c1f14c978","tid":939680,"uid":101732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T10:51:24.000Z","msg":"收到大家意見 咁我分開 留一日去奈良 <br />\n<br />\n神戶有邊間溫泉旅館推介？<br />\n我睇左有間叫陵楓閣 有私人溫泉 食神戶牛 3400一晚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇啲有專車送你去六甲山滑雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd62fc945684b7fa1132eb58dde2adf4ed46051c","tid":939680,"uid":9231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T14:45:38.000Z","msg":"其實鹿真係撚得唔耐<br />\n你要諗下你會有咩做"},{"pid":"03208c88f289d17ebb6a54d90741bbed9e3a0636","tid":939680,"uid":9231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T14:46:24.000Z","msg":"我去左有馬浸溫泉都幾正 有私人風侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292ee1633cbed8b43a03eb0e6e1b15ef9ac8f6c4","tid":939680,"uid":213607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T14:48:51.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"cdc50b6763891169fd95f5095acfe805acdf79f7","tid":939680,"uid":37672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T17:25:52.000Z","msg":"1）有紋身唔駛諗浸公眾池<br />\n2）冬天真係好凍 你未必想咁長時間係室外<br />\n3）鐘意睇風景睇日本風寺廟京都就住一/兩日啦<br />\n4）大阪市內3日夠玩 1日環球1日行a地點街1日行b地點<br />\n5）奈良玩鹿 好多鹿屎 帶對平鞋果日著<br />\n6）問你女朋友想做咩多 你plan完佢話唔鐘意都係無意思<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa529bd8e7a64c984edba15b9deff76b7ad9c28","tid":939680,"uid":214747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T18:31:56.000Z","msg":"有冇人住過RELIEF心齋橋菲利斯酒店 (HOTEL FELICE SHINSAIBASHI By RELIEF)？有冇評價可以比下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見到agoda話房有燒肉味同有塵 同近夜總會 係咪可以唔洗考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見佢400幾蚊夜幾平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d908beb858442763c5c0dcafdeecdc1e562e26f8","tid":939680,"uid":37672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aa529bd8e7a64c984edba15b9deff76b7ad9c28","tid":939680,"uid":214747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T18:31:56.000Z","msg":"有冇人住過RELIEF心齋橋菲利斯酒店 (HOTEL FELICE SHINSAIBASHI By RELIEF)？有冇評價可以比下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見到agoda話房有燒肉味同有塵 同近夜總會 係咪可以唔洗考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見佢400幾蚊夜幾平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T03:12:01.000Z","msg":"400幾如果淡季唔係平 普通價"},{"pid":"3cae62bc4bcdc63362c75565ac296f74a3a4446a","tid":939680,"uid":214747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d908beb858442763c5c0dcafdeecdc1e562e26f8","tid":939680,"uid":37672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aa529bd8e7a64c984edba15b9deff76b7ad9c28","tid":939680,"uid":214747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T18:31:56.000Z","msg":"有冇人住過RELIEF心齋橋菲利斯酒店 (HOTEL FELICE SHINSAIBASHI By RELIEF)？有冇評價可以比下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見到agoda話房有燒肉味同有塵 同近夜總會 係咪可以唔洗考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見佢400幾蚊夜幾平<img src=\"/assets/faces